    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Bacta Technician.</strong></em> You know the temporary boost at-will tech power. When you reach 3rd level, you can cast the bacta pack tech power once per day. When you reach 5th level, you can also cast the kolto dispenser tech power once per day. Your techcasting ability is Intelligence. You do not require use of a wristpad for this power.</p>",
